"title": "8273: holiness, ethical aspects of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8273: holiness, ethical aspects of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Behaviour that reflects the holy character of God himself is to be expressed in both social and personal dimensions of life.</p>\n<h2>Holiness in practice is a reflection of God's own character</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:15-1Pet1:16\">1PE 1:15–1:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:44-Lev11:45\">LEV 11:44–11:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:2\">LEV 19:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:7\">LEV 20:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:24\">EPH 4:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:3\">1JN 3:3</a></p>\n<h2>Holiness demands a different way of life</h2>\n<h3>Shunning practices that defile</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev18:1-Lev18:3\">LEV 18:1–18:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:11-Eph5:12\">EPH 5:11–5:12</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:22\">1TI 5:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev18:21-Lev18:24\">LEV 18:21–18:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev18:29-Lev18:30\">LEV 18:29–18:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:1-Lev20:3\">LEV 20:1–20:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:6-Lev20:7\">LEV 20:6–20:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:23-Lev20:26\">LEV 20:23–20:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev21:7\">LEV 21:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:17-2Cor7:1\">2CO 6:17–7:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:19-Gal5:21\">GAL 5:19–5:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:24\">GAL 5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:3-Eph5:7\">EPH 5:3–5:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:5-Col3:10\">COL 3:5–3:10</a></p>\n<h3>Obedience to God's law</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:7-Lev20:8\">LEV 20:7–20:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev18:4-Lev18:5\">LEV 18:4–18:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:37\">LEV 19:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:25\">DEU 6:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:9\">DEU 28:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:9\">PSA 119:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:12\">ROM 7:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:22\">1PE 1:22</a></p>\n<h2>Holiness is expressed in social behaviour</h2>\n<h3>Care for the disadvantaged</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:9-Lev19:10\">LEV 19:9–19:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:14\">LEV 19:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:33-Lev19:34\">LEV 19:33–19:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:3-1Tim5:4\">1TI 5:3–5:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:8\">1TI 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:27\">JAS 1:27</a></p>\n<h3>A concern for truth and justice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:15-Lev19:16\">LEV 19:15–19:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:11-Lev19:13\">LEV 19:11–19:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:35-Lev19:37\">LEV 19:35–19:37</a></p>\n<h3>Loving one's neighbour</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:18\">LEV 19:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:16-Lev19:17\">LEV 19:16–19:17</a> <em>Most of the OT law can be seen as an expression of holiness.</em></p>\n<h2>Holiness is expressed in family and sexual relations</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:3-1Thess4:7\">1TH 4:3–4:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev18:5-Lev18:20\">LEV 18:5–18:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev18:22-Lev18:23\">LEV 18:22–18:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:3\">LEV 19:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:9\">LEV 20:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:3\">EPH 5:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:13-1Cor6:15\">1CO 6:13–6:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:18-1Cor6:19\">1CO 6:18–6:19</a></p>\n<h2>Holiness is seen in personal character</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:12\">COL 3:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:23-Eph4:24\">EPH 4:23–4:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:32-Eph5:2\">EPH 4:32–5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:22\">2TI 2:22</a></p>",
